\section{The College of Water Magics (Ver 1.2)}
d56 1
a56 1
Adept is surrounded by mist, fog or is standing in the rain & +5 \\
d243 1
a243 1
\emph{Storage:} Investment \\
d354 1
a354 1
\emph{Duration:} 5 days (+5 / Rank) \\
d359 1
a359 1
\emph{Target:} Object \\
d362 6
a367 5
This spell protects any affected object completely from all forms of
non-magical water damage. It works on any item less than or equal to 5
pounds (+ 10 / Rank) in weight. Thus, written scrolls would not run,
steel would not rust, potions would not dilute, clothing would not get
wet etc.
d461 1
a461 1
\emph{Storage:} Investment, Magical Trap \\
