d356 1
a356 1
\emph{Duration:} 5 days (+5/Rank) \\
d361 1
a361 1
\emph{Target:} Object or Entity \\
d364 5
a368 1
This spell protects any effected object completely from all forms of non-magical water damage. It works on any item less than or equal to 5 pounds (+10/Rank) in weight. Thus, written scrolls would not run, steel would not rust, potions would not dilute, clothing would not get wet etc.
